%[text] Constructing selection matrix $\\mathbf{A\_{\\mathit{(m.g)\\times(m.w)}}}\\in\\mathbb{R}^{m.g\\times m.w}$:
% Given variables:
m; % total number of diseases
w; % total number of global platforms
